{"tid":936284,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[汗少]行路掘sweatcoin黎到香港喇喂!","createTime":"2018-12-10T15:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T01:26:44.000Z","uid":18627,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"546f26f160d5bfc453e37841790fbe255533e214","tid":936284,"uid":18627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"大家有無想過行路都可以賺錢? 如有看過英國劇集《黑鏡》(Black mirror) 的朋友， 或許會記得其中一集講述人們踏單車賺取點數以換取日用品或獎賞。上年就有英國初創公司推出類似概念的虛擬貨幣：Sweatcoin(汗幣)，讓用家以步行或跑步方或賺取點數，從而然換取禮品或金錢，於英美大受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n虛擬貨幣 Sweatcoin 賺錢原理<br />\nSweatcoin 由 3 位英國人發明，原意是鼓勵用家堅持做運動、減肥，讓他們覺得每一步都可以得到回報。透過 Sweatcoin，用家每步行、跑 1,000 步就會得到1個「汗幣」，按目前市價，1個汗幣約值0.05美元 (約0.39元港幣)，汗幣可以兌換 app 内合作商家提供的商品、服務，亦可以當作慈善捐出去，或轉贈給其他用戶。不過汗幣未有正式的交易平台，用戶需透過社交平台或討論區放售，如Reddit討論區展期有人討論汗幣，最新亦有人開始公開交易。<br />\n<br />\n創辦人稱「汗幣」跟「比特幣」一樣採用了防篡改的區塊鏈技術來管理，他們最終目標是將汗幣匯率跟英鎊掛鉤，如「汗幣」有更多用戶，將來更有機會當作保險公司、健康相關企業的支付工具。不過，程式暫時只能在美國、英國等地方下載（使用App Store下載時，需轉換地區，亦支援Android平台），香港用戶在登記賬戶時，須把「地點」轉到英國才會見到換領禮品的相關資訊。雖然未知汗幣日後能否在全球普及，但這種賺取虛擬貨幣的方式不用付出真金白銀，也不用像Bitcoin或以太幣等添置電腦「挖幣」，一試無妨。禮品選擇的類型亦相當多類型，包括電子產品如iPhone、Fitbit，或一些雜誌、課程，又或是PayPal現金。一部iPhone X索價20,000汗幣。<br />\n<br />\n快速儲汗幣招數：<br />\n1.每日在Offer page完成Daily Bonus，看30秒廣告即可獲1汗幣；<br />\n2.當朋友使用你的推薦連結下載並登入，便可獲5汗幣；<br />\n3.關閉「省電模式」後能計算的步數比較多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.comebusiness.com/zh/newsdetail/504/%E6%B1%97%E5%B9%A3App-%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E8%B7%91%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E8%B7%AF%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%A2%E6%94%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.comebusiness.com%2Fzh%2Fnewsdetail%2F504%2F%25E6%25B1%2597%25E5%25B9%25A3App-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25B7%2591%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258C%25A2%25E6%2594%25B6&d=86ABpKDzLjZEwZBvaFsFrwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=45674395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.comebusiness.com/zh/newsdetail/504/%E6%B1%97%E5%B9%A3App-%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E8%B7%91%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E8%B7%AF%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%A2%E6%94%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n巴絲可以用下面條invite link download個apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sweatcoinapp.uk/i/geoffrey327225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsweatcoinapp.uk%2Fi%2Fgeoffrey327225&d=86ABpKDzLjZEwZBvaFsFrwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2726a492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">sweatcoinapp.uk/i/geoffrey327225</a> <br />\n<br />\nCheck out this free app 👆 It pays to walk!"},{"pid":"fcdedb6095b5a561072b24844877df2297947659","tid":936284,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"行路撚又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9664e7699e3aa673aef92be9cf2879f6bbd99d25","tid":936284,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:04:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"87e2ba4680f6e56773d8b94900364c31524b0759","tid":936284,"uid":191073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"諗起數碼暴龍搖搖機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58dfd5d56e0108e888326a4b753291a49899f2d","tid":936284,"uid":13275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"留名睇大陸pokemon go 飛行狗一晚幾萬幣"},{"pid":"10b864136c29962034db5a7f86295007fca8998f","tid":936284,"uid":12394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:07:41.000Z","msg":"條link幫樓主刷幣 <br />\n<br />\n個app d iPhone 20000coins 要兩年內刷到，每日行爆哂仲要拉勁多人用個apps 先夠coins <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f2e04e0e71281b481547adf581fc9e226424e3","tid":936284,"uid":12394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58dfd5d56e0108e888326a4b753291a49899f2d","tid":936284,"uid":13275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"留名睇大陸pokemon go 飛行狗一晚幾萬幣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:08:12.000